        "Description": "Good Afternoon 47\r\rToday&apos;s target is Grace Miller. Better known as Sierra Knox&apos;s Lead Mechanic. Or how we know her, the cheater. Apprently she was caught adding Octane Boost to Sierra&apos;s car to win the 2015 Endurance Race. Now that we have her location its time to put in end to her cheating. We prefer you don&apos;t draw attettion to yourself on camera. And to escape take the medical truck, its &quot;sneakier&quot;. Just obtain the keys thru the doctor analyzing a urinary problem.\r\rGood Luck 47",
